about.summary: Alternative regular expression module, to replace re.

name: regex
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "2016.09.22" %}

package:
    name: regex
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: regex-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/r/regex/regex-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 5831c142d9a5b2447e0c5ee9a77b2aaee2ecbbff1025715ec3c6f6c7fc9b682b

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install

requirements:
    build:
        - python
    run:
        - python

test:
    imports:
        - regex

about:
    home: https://bitbucket.org/mrabarnett/mrab-regex
    license: Python-2.0
    summary: 'Alternative regular expression module, to replace re.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - kwilcox
        - ocefpaf
